data.description: If your desires are to own your little ranch in a quite area, come and see this nice property in the outsides of Lindsay. Quiet country setting just minutes from town. Small and cozy with plenty of room to grow. With pole fencing horse corral. Detached garage with storage room and 12x26 RV carport, all this is on a little bit more than one acre lot, planted with orange trees. Don't hesitate to make your appointment because this property won't last long.
